description: A great winter warmer of a simple homestyle chicken and vegetable soup that can be enjoyed by anyone!
name: Slow Cooker Chicken & Vegetable Soup Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 1L massel low fodmap chicken style stock

recipeInstructions.text: Gather all your ingredients accept for the frozen green beans.

Peel carrots and potatoes. Dice potatoes to a small size and slice carrots to appx 1cm thick. Chop broccoli head into florets. Slice zucchini down the middle lengthwise and slice to appx 1 cm thick. * ** Remember to discard chunky broccoli stalks and vegetable peelings for compost or green waste.
Put all vegetable ingredients into slow cooker including LOW FODMAP stock. Add pepper and give a good stir to mix vegetables.
Put in Chicken fillets and slice in halves. Mix it all about.
Cook on low for 5.5 hours. Stirring a couple of times along the way.
Carefully take the chicken out, shred it, then put it back in the slow cooker along with the frozen green baby beans. Cook for another half hour on low.
